Paper: hep-th/0108093

Date: 2001-08-14

Title: Bulk-Boundary Propagator in Liouville Theory on a Disc

Authors: Kazuo Hosomichi

Comments: 7 pages, LaTeX2e, v2

with TeX)Journal-ref: JHEP 0111 (2001) 044

We study Liouville theory on worldsheets with boundary using the solutions ofKnizhnik-Zamolodchikov equation involving a degenerate representation of theVirasoro algebra. The expression for bulk-boundary propagator on a disc isproposed.